text: Managed to borrow an Android phone… someone else would need to accept the tablet :simple_smile:
I don't need the tablet though.
Somebody else let me know if they want it.
I don't have an android device so I may want it if I can figure out how to set t all up! I'm on my way to class now

For anyone who isn't sure how to set up their android device for development, take a look at these articles.
<https://developer.android.com/tools/device.html>
<https://developer.android.com/tools/help/adb.html>

attachments.title: Using Hardware Devices | Android Developers
attachments.text: When building a mobile application, it's important that you always test your application on a real device before releasing it to users. This page describes how to set up your development environment and Android-powered device for testing and debugging…
